pullrequest.title: Use latest version of subt tunnel staging area

content.raw: we ran into the same problem when testing it out on @{5cf75629ff02b50ea27b2817} computer today. We then did what was suggested: went to the fuel website and downloaded the tar file manually through the UI. After that, we launched simulation again, and the correct version was downloaded. I wonder if something is caching the files.
